# CycleLister frontend environment.
#
# Supabase auth is OPTIONAL for local development. Leave both values empty
# (or delete this file) to run the app with no sign-in gate (dev mode).
#
# To enable the email/password sign-in gate, set BOTH of these to the values
# from your Supabase project (Project Settings -> API):
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
